    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170250/extras/281709b1ab9cb084647a90ca81f4cfb1.avif?t=1772135897\" width=920 height=430 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巫师们本该在深夜啜饮「魔药」、研读古籍，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可惜，某种可怖之物已悄然笼罩他们这瑰丽奇绝的魔法世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >危险！黑暗大军正向魔法高塔进发——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唯有魔法学院的学徒（包括毕业生，偶尔也有导师）能奔出迎战，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一路疾驰至天际尽头，穿越沙漠与群山，直面那胆敢惊扰他们安宁的家伙！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>自动奔跑</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跨越障碍，闪避攻击，从敌人身上拾取战利品。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>弹幕射击</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人朝你开火？你便以魔法还击！一点「弹幕地狱」，恰是唤醒沉睡魔力的最佳良方。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>元进度成长</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对敌人施展法术后，他们有时会留下金币——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无人知晓他们是化作了金币，抑或本就随身携带——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但你可用这些金币解锁全新技能与新巫师。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170250/extras/60f512e56e87ae1f4bb05a89af014412.avif?t=1772135897\" alt=\"\"width=304 height=352 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><u>他們正在逼近！</u></strong></p>",
